1
00:01:33,319 --> 00:01:34,439
You're back.

2
00:01:38,840 --> 00:01:39,599
Leng Qingqiu.

3
00:01:40,920 --> 00:01:42,480
Why did you come here?

4
00:01:43,200 --> 00:01:44,640
I came to chat with you.

5
00:01:44,719 --> 00:01:45,519
Is that not okay?

6
00:01:48,840 --> 00:01:49,920
That batch of medicine...

7
00:01:49,920 --> 00:01:51,319
I've already destroyed it.

8
00:01:51,599 --> 00:01:52,400
I know.

9
00:01:53,040 --> 00:01:54,920
Didn't you hate me the most before?

10
00:01:54,920 --> 00:01:56,120
You'd run away when you saw me.

11
00:01:56,400 --> 00:01:57,680
And now you're...

12
00:01:58,000 --> 00:01:59,799
What are you doing here in the middle of the night?

13
00:01:59,799 --> 00:02:00,599
Are you crazy?

14
00:02:00,599 --> 00:02:02,599
Didn't you use to wish I'd look at you more?

15
00:02:03,120 --> 00:02:04,480
Now I've come to you.

16
00:02:04,840 --> 00:02:06,840
Why pretend to be pure and chaste?

17
00:02:07,040 --> 00:02:07,840
Hypocrite.

18
00:02:10,439 --> 00:02:12,599
I have to find a way to cut ties with her.

19
00:02:20,879 --> 00:02:22,319
Well, since you don't want to leave,

20
00:02:23,120 --> 00:02:24,400
drink this.

21
00:02:24,680 --> 00:02:25,680
Liven things up for me.

22
00:02:29,240 --> 00:02:31,039
You, Leng Qingqiu, have always been proud.

23
00:02:32,000 --> 00:02:33,039
First, you never drink.

24
00:02:33,039 --> 00:02:34,080
Second, you don't take threats.

25
00:02:34,319 --> 00:02:36,280
It's always been me trying to please you.

26
00:02:36,280 --> 00:02:37,280
I don't believe

27
00:02:37,280 --> 00:02:38,840
you can take this humiliation now.

28
00:02:39,680 --> 00:02:40,479
Lu Chengwen,

29
00:02:41,840 --> 00:02:43,039
what do you mean?

30
00:02:48,400 --> 00:02:49,280
I can't feel sorry for her.

31
00:02:50,039 --> 00:02:51,840
I must not be fooled by her puppy eyes.

32
00:02:52,240 --> 00:02:53,520
I can't get tangled up with her.

33
00:02:55,120 --> 00:02:56,400
You can't drink it, right?

34
00:02:57,039 --> 00:02:58,000
Just leave.

35
00:03:11,319 --> 00:03:12,400
I can't be soft-hearted.

36
00:03:26,639 --> 00:03:27,439
Enough.

37
00:03:28,319 --> 00:03:30,000
If you can't drink, don't pretend.

38
00:03:30,719 --> 00:03:31,919
You can scold me

39
00:03:32,199 --> 00:03:33,479
or hit me a few times.

40
00:03:35,919 --> 00:03:36,719
Just go.

41
00:03:39,840 --> 00:03:40,599
What are you doing?

42
00:03:41,840 --> 00:03:42,639
Leng Qingqiu,

43
00:03:42,800 --> 00:03:44,039
calm down, okay?

44
00:03:46,240 --> 00:03:48,000
You are a woman with your own career,

45
00:03:48,000 --> 00:03:49,319
an excellent woman.

46
00:03:49,719 --> 00:03:50,840
There's no need to waste all your time

47
00:03:50,840 --> 00:03:52,400
on a scumbag like me.

48
00:03:53,520 --> 00:03:55,319
But you chased me for three years.

49
00:03:56,000 --> 00:03:56,639
Why?

50
00:03:56,639 --> 00:03:58,639
Now that I've agreed,

51
00:03:59,039 --> 00:04:00,840
you want me to leave you.

52
00:04:05,840 --> 00:04:07,000
Because...

53
00:04:07,800 --> 00:04:08,840
I'm tired.

54
00:04:08,840 --> 00:04:09,840
I'm annoyed.

55
00:04:12,120 --> 00:04:13,319
I'm turned off.

56
00:04:22,839 --> 00:04:23,639
Fine.

57
00:04:26,279 --> 00:04:27,319
Then I'll go.

58
00:04:39,680 --> 00:04:40,639
Bastard.

59
00:04:43,519 --> 00:04:45,639
As long as you feel better scolding me.

60
00:04:46,199 --> 00:04:47,240
Hurry up and leave.

61
00:04:52,639 --> 00:04:53,839
Do you

62
00:04:54,800 --> 00:04:56,319
hate me a lot now?

63
00:04:59,800 --> 00:05:00,600
Yeah.

64
00:05:03,680 --> 00:05:04,680
How is that possible?

65
00:05:05,279 --> 00:05:06,879
Such a lovely and touching beauty,

66
00:05:07,000 --> 00:05:08,279
