97
00:07:48,439 --> 00:07:49,600
If you really dare to do that,

98
00:07:49,720 --> 00:07:51,079
I'll kill you.

99
00:07:58,720 --> 00:08:00,319
If you're going to keep standing in the way,

100
00:08:00,439 --> 00:08:01,439
then please

101
00:08:01,879 --> 00:08:03,040
help me grab that.

102
00:08:19,040 --> 00:08:21,040
This Leng Qingqiu seems pretty nice.

103
00:08:21,439 --> 00:08:23,319
She's not that unreasonable after all.

104
00:08:24,800 --> 00:08:25,600
You brat!

105
00:08:26,439 --> 00:08:28,040
Did you do something bad again?

106
00:08:42,080 --> 00:08:42,879
Mom!

107
00:08:47,679 --> 00:08:48,440
Mom,

108
00:08:48,440 --> 00:08:49,480
