114
00:08:57,120 --> 00:08:57,320
Mom,

115
00:08:57,320 --> 00:08:58,200
listen to me.

116
00:08:58,200 --> 00:08:58,639
Explain?

117
00:08:58,639 --> 00:08:59,240
I...

118
00:08:59,639 --> 00:09:00,639
I didn't do anything last night!

119
00:09:00,639 --> 00:09:01,039
I...

120
00:09:01,039 --> 00:09:01,919
I want you to explain!

121
00:09:02,600 --> 00:09:03,320
I want you to explain!

122
00:09:03,320 --> 00:09:04,120
Mom!

123
00:09:05,440 --> 00:09:06,240
Qingqiu,

124
00:09:06,399 --> 00:09:08,480
