128
00:09:12,440 --> 00:09:14,600
Our families will discuss the wedding properly.

129
00:09:14,840 --> 00:09:15,600
This porridge is good.

130
00:09:15,600 --> 00:09:16,320
Have some.

131
00:09:16,320 --> 00:09:16,919
It'll help you sober up.

132
00:09:16,919 --> 00:09:17,720
Thank you, Auntie.

133
00:09:26,120 --> 00:09:27,440
You still have the nerve to eat?

134
00:09:28,120 --> 00:09:28,799
No,

135
00:09:28,799 --> 00:09:29,600
Mom,

136
00:09:29,600 --> 00:09:30,840
let me serve you some.

137
00:09:31,120 --> 00:09:32,039
You have some too.

138
00:09:32,200 --> 00:09:33,080
What's wrong, son?

139
00:09:33,200 --> 00:09:34,320
Did you change your personality today?

140
00:09:35,000 --> 00:09:35,679
Well,

141
00:09:35,679 --> 00:09:37,200
I haven't seen you for days.

142
00:09:37,240 --> 00:09:38,200
I missed you.

143
00:09:38,840 --> 00:09:40,000
He's quite filial.

144
00:09:40,200 --> 00:09:41,399
You little brat.

145
00:09:41,399 --> 00:09:42,080
I'll eat later.

146
00:09:42,080 --> 00:09:43,440
Qingqiu,

147
00:09:43,600 --> 00:09:44,639
you two have a good chat.

148
00:09:44,720 --> 00:09:46,440
The servants are still cooking in the kitchen.

149
00:09:46,440 --> 00:09:47,799
I'll go see how it's going.

150
00:09:48,000 --> 00:09:48,240
Yeah.

151
00:09:48,240 --> 00:09:48,600
Okay,

152
00:09:48,600 --> 00:09:49,440
Auntie.

153
00:10:17,039 --> 00:10:18,799
How can there be such a beautiful woman?

154
00:10:19,200 --> 00:10:20,240
Just watching her eat

155
00:10:20,240 --> 00:10:21,720
