207
00:12:02,120 --> 00:12:02,600
Scumbag.

208
00:12:03,120 --> 00:12:04,000
Qingqiu,

209
00:12:05,440 --> 00:12:06,320
what's wrong?

210
00:12:06,840 --> 00:12:07,639
What?

211
00:12:07,720 --> 00:12:08,799
Trying to coax me?

212
00:12:09,720 --> 00:12:11,320
I won't forgive you.

213
00:12:11,600 --> 00:12:12,639
I'm fine.

214
00:12:12,720 --> 00:12:13,879
I'm just afraid

215
00:12:13,879 --> 00:12:16,240
